      "recording_attendee_id": "de5ab578-cc05-49ec-9f80-d2d4b7df4de4",
      "order_number": 2,
      "text": "Yes sir,"
    },
    {
      "id": "a80792a1-b92b-4c8a-824b-25c92236f53e",
      "recording_id": "3a4f99f6-47b9-4612-a52d-d6d904f0812d",
      "end_time": 6.98,
      "start_time": 4.46,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9ae12e63-c5d3-429b-abce-b62eba6ddad9",
      "order_number": 3,
      "text": "Hey, this is fred calling from rentable, how are you?"
    },
    {
      "id": "a80792a1-b92b-4c8a-824b-25c92236f53e",
      "recording_id": "3a4f99f6-47b9-4612-a52d-d6d904f0812d",
      "end_time": 8.51,
      "start_time": 7.33,
      "recording_attendee_id": "de5ab578-cc05-49ec-9f80-d2d4b7df4de4",
      "order_number": 4,
      "text": "I'm good, how are you?"
    },
    {
      "id": "a80792a1-b92b-4c8a-824b-25c92236f53e",
      "recording_id": "3a4f99f6-47b9-4612-a52d-d6d904f0812d",
      "end_time": 14.31,
      "start_time": 8.52,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9ae12e63-c5d3-429b-abce-b62eba6ddad9",
      "order_number": 5,
      "text": "Good, good. Um I sent you a few emails, Not sure if you uh were able to open them. But"
    },
    {
      "id": "a80792a1-b92b-4c8a-824b-25c92236f53e",
      "recording_id": "3a4f99f6-47b9-4612-a52d-d6d904f0812d",
      "end_time": 15.07,
      "start_time": 14.29,
      "recording_attendee_id": "de5ab578-cc05-49ec-9f80-d2d4b7df4de4",
      "order_number": 6,
      "text": "Yeah,"
    },
    {
      "id": "a80792a1-b92b-4c8a-824b-25c92236f53e",
      "recording_id": "3a4f99f6-47b9-4612-a52d-d6d904f0812d",
      "end_time": 14.81,
      "start_time": 14.31,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9ae12e63-c5d3-429b-abce-b62eba6ddad9",
      "order_number": 7,
      "text": "um"
    },
    {
      "id": "a80792a1-b92b-4c8a-824b-25c92236f53e",
      "recording_id": "3a4f99f6-47b9-4612-a52d-d6d904f0812d",
      "end_time": 27.37,
      "start_time": 15.07,
      "recording_attendee_id": "de5ab578-cc05-49ec-9f80-d2d4b7df4de4",
      "order_number": 8,
      "text": "I I saw them um and I appreciate you reaching out. I just you know, nothing's really has changed since. Um I think I spoke with your colleague so um"
    },
    {
      "id": "a80792a1-b92b-4c8a-824b-25c92236f53e",
      "recording_id": "3a4f99f6-47b9-4612-a52d-d6d904f0812d",
      "end_time": 36.99,
      "start_time": 27.06,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9ae12e63-c5d3-429b-abce-b62eba6ddad9",
      "order_number": 9,
      "text": "do you mind me asking what the what what was the reason that you um didn't want to make the move? A ton has changed over here? That's why I was just uh reaching out."
    },
    {
      "id": "a80792a1-b92b-4c8a-824b-25c92236f53e",
      "recording_id": "3a4f99f6-47b9-4612-a52d-d6d904f0812d",
      "end_time": 53.45,
      "start_time": 37.79,
      "recording_attendee_id": "de5ab578-cc05-49ec-9f80-d2d4b7df4de4",
      "order_number": 10,
      "text": "well so I think this is a similar story to you know at since the pandemic, right? So there's a lack of supply more than there is a lack of demand. So we have zero problems leasing stuff out."
    },
    {
      "id": "a80792a1-b92b-4c8a-824b-25c92236f53e",
      "recording_id": "3a4f99f6-47b9-4612-a52d-d6d904f0812d",
      "end_time": 54.4,
      "start_time": 53.73,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9ae12e63-c5d3-429b-abce-b62eba6ddad9",
      "order_number": 11,
      "text": "Okay."
    },
    {
      "id": "a80792a1-b92b-4c8a-824b-25c92236f53e",
      "recording_id": "3a4f99f6-47b9-4612-a52d-d6d904f0812d",
      "end_time": 61.26,
      "start_time": 54.15,
      "recording_attendee_id": "de5ab578-cc05-49ec-9f80-d2d4b7df4de4",
      "order_number": 12,
      "text": "Um And we're we're just desperate to get any house or apartments to rent out."
    },
    {
      "id": "a80792a1-b92b-4c8a-824b-25c92236f53e",
      "recording_id": "3a4f99f6-47b9-4612-a52d-d6d904f0812d",
      "end_time": 62.62,
      "start_time": 61.9,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9ae12e63-c5d3-429b-abce-b62eba6ddad9",
      "order_number": 13,
      "text": "Okay."
    },
    {
      "id": "a80792a1-b92b-4c8a-824b-25c92236f53e",
      "recording_id": "3a4f99f6-47b9-4612-a52d-d6d904f0812d",
      "end_time": 62.68,
      "start_time": 61.91,
      "recording_attendee_id": "de5ab578-cc05-49ec-9f80-d2d4b7df4de4",
      "order_number": 14,
      "text": "Um"
    },
    {
      "id": "a80792a1-b92b-4c8a-824b-25c92236f53e",
      "recording_id": "3a4f99f6-47b9-4612-a52d-d6d904f0812d",
      "end_time": 64.43,
      "start_time": 62.62,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9ae12e63-c5d3-429b-abce-b62eba6ddad9",
      "order_number": 15,
      "text": "So no need basically that makes"
