      "start_time": 65.32,
      "recording_attendee_id": "de5ab578-cc05-49ec-9f80-d2d4b7df4de4",
      "order_number": 18,
      "text": "Yeah. Yeah. Yeah."
    },
    {
      "id": "a80792a1-b92b-4c8a-824b-25c92236f53e",
      "recording_id": "3a4f99f6-47b9-4612-a52d-d6d904f0812d",
      "end_time": 76.72,
      "start_time": 67.08,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9ae12e63-c5d3-429b-abce-b62eba6ddad9",
      "order_number": 19,
      "text": "Um any idea or I guess no one really knows what it's gonna change. But do you know what do you think a better time for me to reach out I guess would be a couple of months at this point?"
    },
    {
      "id": "a80792a1-b92b-4c8a-824b-25c92236f53e",
      "recording_id": "3a4f99f6-47b9-4612-a52d-d6d904f0812d",
      "end_time": 91.19,
      "start_time": 76.89,
      "recording_attendee_id": "de5ab578-cc05-49ec-9f80-d2d4b7df4de4",
      "order_number": 20,
      "text": "Yeah. It'll probably be after the election in november next year because I think that's when I think the um the change is gonna happen and a lot of stuff is gonna start unraveling right"
    },
