      "recording_attendee_id": "9ae12e63-c5d3-429b-abce-b62eba6ddad9",
      "order_number": 28,
      "text": "tell me that you're gonna give me nightmares as a person."
    },
    {
      "id": "a80792a1-b92b-4c8a-824b-25c92236f53e",
      "recording_id": "3a4f99f6-47b9-4612-a52d-d6d904f0812d",
      "end_time": 139.97,
      "start_time": 119.71,
      "recording_attendee_id": "de5ab578-cc05-49ec-9f80-d2d4b7df4de4",
      "order_number": 29,
      "text": "yeah, I'm not trying to make your life more difference. You know, it's tough for me too because I don't make anything from renting stuff out. I make all my money from uh I'm signing new houses. I'm struggling to that city help but yeah, it's just kind of hunker down and wait it out for a few uh few months."
