      "recording_id": "3a4f99f6-47b9-4612-a52d-d6d904f0812d",
      "end_time": 157.88,
      "start_time": 141.2,
      "recording_attendee_id": "9ae12e63-c5d3-429b-abce-b62eba6ddad9",
      "order_number": 30,
      "text": "Yeah, that makes sense. Alright. But yeah, but I'm not gonna, there's no need, I'm not gonna try to show you on it, so I won't wait, I won't waste any of your time. But uh if you have my email, if anything changes, let me know if not I won't wait until november to email you. But uh"
    },
